  "content": "  <p>5-persona review, session history, agent coordination. The process and the product grew together.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      <span>Lim Chun Zhe</span>\n      <span>4 / 10</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n<!-- SLIDE 4 — THE LOOP EVOLVED                        -->\n<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n<div class=\"slide slide-4\">\n  <div class=\"slide-inner\">\n    <div class=\"slide-label\">The Process</div>\n    <div class=\"slide-title\">The Loop <span class=\"hl-green\">Evolved</span></div>\n    <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">Day 1 vs. today.</div>\n\n    <div class=\"compare-cols\">\n      <div class=\"compare-col\" style=\"border-top: 3px solid var(--text-muted);\">\n        <h3 style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\">Week 1</h3>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-amber\">1</span> Brainstorm + Design</div>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-amber\">2</span> Build</div>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-amber\">3</span> Try to record decisions</div>\n        <div class=\"step-item\" style=\"color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; border-bottom: none;\">(some got missed)</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"compare-col\" style=\"border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-green);\">\n        <h3 class=\"hl-green\">Today</h3>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-blue\">1</span> Search what's decided</div>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-purple\">2</span> Brainstorm + Design</div>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-amber\">3</span> Build + Test</div>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-green\">4</span> 5-Persona Review</div>\n        <div class=\"step-item\"><span class=\"step-num hl-cyan\">5</span> Record into corvia</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"loop-insight\">\n      The process and the product co-evolved. Each capability added to corvia improved how the next one got built.\n    </div>",
